  "html": "<p class=\"\">I love being able to reference the technical details when editing photography—aperture, shutter speed, ISO, all the little choices that go into making a photograph. But most photo prints completely ignore this data, treating it like metadata to be hidden away in EXIF tags that nobody ever sees. So I made a little app to add the EXIF data to the margins of prints you might get from CVS, Walgreens, or Wal-Mart (don't use them for photo prints, I learned the hard way.)</p>\n<p class=\"\"></p><figure role=\"figure\" aria-label=\"EXIF Photo Printer application displaying five family photos with options to regenerate layouts or save prints at 4x6 size.\" class=\"\"><img src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755098311/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.18.12_AM.png\" alt=\"EXIF Photo Printer application displaying five family photos with options to regenerate layouts or save prints at 4x6 size.\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" srcset=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_640/v1755098311/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.18.12_AM.png 640w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_960/v1755098311/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.18.12_AM.png 960w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1280/v1755098311/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.18.12_AM.png 1280w, https://res.cloudinary.com/ejf/image/upload/c_scale,f_auto,q_auto:good,w_1920/v1755098311/screenshot_2025-08-13_at_11.18.12_AM.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 430px) 92vw, (max-width: 768px) 85vw, 900px\" title=\"EXIF Photo Printer application displaying five family photos with options to regenerate layouts or save prints at 4x6 size.\" style=\"background-color:#222222;background-image:url(&#x22;data:image/jpeg;base64,&#x22;);background-size:cover;background-position:center;--splay-rot:2.74deg;\" width=\"2400\" height=\"1800\" data-dimensions=\"2400×1800\" class=\"img-full my-8 rounded-sm img-splay w-full mx-auto py-4\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"><figcaption class=\"\">EXIF Photo Printer application displaying five family photos with options to regenerate layouts or save prints at 4x6 size.</figcaption></figure><p class=\"\"></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"https://github.com/ejfox/exif-printer-simple\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group inline-flex items-center text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400\" data-preview-url=\"https://github.com/ejfox/exif-printer-simple\">exif-printer<svg class=\"inline-block w-4 h-4 ml-1 opacity-50 dark:opacity-75 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity align-text-bottom\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentColor\" d=\"M12 .297c-6.63 0-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.303 3.438 9.8 8.205 11.385c.6.113.82-.258.82-.577c0-.285-.01-1.04-.015-2.04c-3.338.724-4.042-1.61-4.042-1.61C4.422 18.07 3.633 17.7 3.633 17.7c-1.087-.744.084-.729.084-.729c1.205.084 1.838 1.236 1.838 1.236c1.07 1.835 2.809 1.305 3.495.998c.108-.776.417-1.305.76-1.605c-2.665-.3-5.466-1.332-5.466-5.93c0-1.31.465-2.38 1.235-3.22c-.135-.303-.54-1.523.105-3.176c0 0 1.005-.322 3.3 1.23c.96-.267 1.98-.399 3-.405c1.02.006 2.04.138 3 .405c2.28-1.552 3.285-1.23 3.285-1.23c.645 1.653.24 2.873.12 3.176c.765.84 1.23 1.91 1.23 3.22c0 4.61-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.92c.42.36.81 1.096.81 2.22c0 1.606-.015 2.896-.015 3.286c0 .315.21.69.825.57C20.565 22.092 24 17.592 24 12.297c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12\" class=\"\"></path></svg></a>: Creates printable photos with camera settings displayed in the borders - a photographer's tool that treats metadata as part of the art.</p>",
